This is how to get_odd_collatz of n:
   Remember that odds is []
   Remember that x is 1
   Do this n times:
      When remainder of x and 2 is 1, then:
         Remember that y is x
         Do this 1000 times:
            When y is 1, then:
               Add odds to x
               Leave the loop
            End when
            When remainder of y and 2 is 0, then:
               Remember that y is quotient of y and 2
            But, if not:
               Remember that y is sum of (product of 3 and y) and 1
            End when
         End do
      End when
      Increase x
   End do
   The answer is odds
